cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper deals with image processing and learning from image samples to generate textual descriptions. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper involves natural language generation and grammar-based description synthesis. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses supervised learning and classification algorithms to learn room categories and generate descriptions. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper involves learning from image samples and using the learned annotations to generate descriptions. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper deals with providing accessibility to visually impaired individuals, which falls under the domain of human-computer interaction.
